<manpage>
    <volume> 常用数据结构 </volume>
    <interface>AStringBuf</interface>
    <method> IndexOfChar </method>

    <description>
        <para> 报告指定Char32字符在此对象中的第一个匹配项的索引。</para>
    </description>
    <syntax>
        <return_val> Int32 </return_val>
        <modifier>const</modifier>
        <parameters>
        <api_param>
            <param_type>Char32</param_type>
            <param_name> ch </param_name>
            <param_note>
                <para> 指定字符。 </para>
            </param_note>
        </api_param>
        <api_param>
            <param_type>StringCase</param_type>
            <param_name> stringCase  </param_name>
            <param_default> StringCase_Sensitive</param_default>
            <param_note>
                <para> 是否区分大小写标志。参见<link url="../../others/StringCase.htm">StringCase</link>枚举类型说明。(StringCase_Insensitive暂不支持) </para>
            </param_note>
        </api_param>  
        <api_param>
            <param_type>Encoding</param_type>
            <param_name>encoding</param_name>
            <param_default> Encoding_Default</param_default>
            <param_note>
                <para> 指定编码格式。参见<link url="../../others/Encoding.htm">Encoding</link>枚举类型说明。</para>
            </param_note>
        </api_param>           
        </parameters>        
    </syntax>
    <return>
        <para>返回字符在AStringBuf对象字符串中首次出现的索引值，若没出现则返回-1。</para>
    </return>
     <remarks>
        <para>如果AStringBuf对象字符串指针NULL或内容为空，则返回-1。</para>
    </remarks>
<example>
<pre>
AStringBuf_&lt;10&gt; asbuf;  
asbuf.Copy("abcabc");
Char32 searchtemp1 = 'b';
Char32 searchtemp2 = 'x';
CConsole::WriteLine(asbuf.IndexOfChar(searchtemp1));  //Display : 1
CConsole::WriteLine(asbuf.IndexOfChar(searchtemp2));  //Display : -1
</pre>
</example>

